Package server.commands

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CAdmins
    Show server and room admins.
    CBans
    Show bans from room or server, depending on the user who's using the command.
    CDesc
    Shows room's and server's description.
    CHelp
    Show available commands.
    CJoinroom
    Join a room.
    CKick
    Kick user from room, requires mode 1.
    CLeaveroom
    Leave current room.
    CMode
    Get mode/Change user mode, requires mode 3.
    CMotd
    Show server/room message of the day.
    CMutes
    Show muted users in room, requires mode 1.
    CPrivmsg
    Send a private message to user.
    CQuit
    Disconnect from server.
    CRoomban
    Ban user from room.
    CRoomdesc
    Set room description, requires mode 2.
    CRoomlogin
    Login as a room moderator or admin
    CRoommode
    Set user mode to 0 or 1, requires mode 2.
    CRoommotd
    Change room's message of the day
    CRoommute
    Mute user from talking in a room, requires mode 1.
    CRoomnotice
    Sends a notification to every user in the room, requires mode 1.
    CRoompassword
    Set room password, requires mode 2
    CRooms
    Shows all the rooms in server
    CRoomunban
    Unban user from room, requires mode 1.
    CRoomunmute
    Remove user's room mute, requires mode 1.
    CRules
    Shows the rules.
    CServerban
    Ban user from server, requires mode 3.
    CServerdesc
    Set server description, requires mode 3.
    CServerkick
    Kick user from server, requires mode 3.
    CServerlogin
    Login as a server admin (mode 3)
    CServermotd
    Change server's message of the day
    CServernotice
    Send a message to every user on server, requires mode 3.
    CServerpassword
    Change server password, requires mode 3.
    CServerunban
    Unban user from server, requires mode 3.
    CUsername
    Get username/User can change their username with this command.
    CUsers
    Command that lists all the users in the current room.
